$50




Maximum Subsequent Premiums (per policy year after 1st policy anniversary)
$25,000 (Non-qualified), 

Lesser of $60,000 or IRS

Contribution limit (Qualified)




Maximum Cumulative Premiums
$1,000,000 (0-80)

$500,000 (Over age 80)




Annual Mortality and Expense Fee and Administrative Charge (M&E&A)1
1.15% (Policy Value Death Benefit)1.30% (Return of Premium Death Benefit)1.50% (Annual Step-Up Death Benefit)




Annual Service Charge
$502 (but no more than 2% of policy value)




